comments.body:
@quantum77, I have empathy for your frustration, especially when being stuck and seeking help.

I cannot fulfill the expectation to reply to all questions in IRC. On some days, that would be a full-time job. Oftentimes, community members are able to answer questions that I wouldn't be able to. Opening an issue, in many cases, is a better option as it allows for asynchronous communication. Simple issues are easily answered in IRC but yours seem rather complex, especially as it may be unrelated to Podman; I have no expertise at all in nftables or networking.

Talking about your issue.  Please follow the required issue template which asks for a reproducer along with providing the environment data of `podman info`. Without that, it'll be hard to know what's going on.
